    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 justify-center items-center">
      <%= image_tag("method-radicals.png") %>
      <h3 class="flex flex-col gap-4 justify-center text-center text-3xl font-semibold">Radicals</h3>
      <p class="text-center">Kanji is great, but it’s not very useful without vocabulary. Learn over 6,000 Japanese words, all carefully validated by a human to be common or useful.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 justify-center items-center">
      <%= image_tag("method-kanji.png") %>
      <h3 class="flex flex-col gap-4 justify-center text-center text-3xl font-semibold">Kanji</h3>
      <p class="text-center">Learn over 2,000 kanji, hand-picked and cleverly ordered, so you can learn the kanji meanings and readings more efficiently. A Japanese schoolchild will spend eight years doing what you can do in a year and a half.</p>
