      <p class="text-center">Radicals, kanji, and vocabulary are taught to you through lessons using mnemonics. Practice learned items via reviews until recalling them is second nature.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 justify-center items-center">
      <%= image_tag("method-srs.png") %>
      <h3 class="flex flex-col gap-4 justify-center text-center text-3xl font-semibold">Spaced Repetition System</h3>
      <p class="text-center">WaniKani is more than just flashcards. Our SRS algorithm adjusts time between reviews for each individual item, calculated by your last session. You will see a radical, kanji, or vocabulary in your reviews at the optimal time for you, not anybody else.</p>
